UPDATE public.blog_posts SET content = '<p>A Conversational Intelligence API empowers host platforms to extract actionable insights from customer interactions by analyzing speech patterns, sentiment, and intent through AI-driven processing. While standard tools process calls and chats, Voicera elevates this with multimodal capabilities—enabling your platform to detect sincerity and emotions 30% more accurately than human analysis. This allows Sales, HR, and Legal platforms to offer "Trust" as a feature.</p>

<h2>What is a Conversational Intelligence API?</h2>

<div>
<div>
<p>A Conversational Intelligence API refers to RESTful services that transcribe, analyze, and derive business value from dialogues across voice, text, or video channels. Using NLP, ASR, and machine learning,these APIs handle core functions like speech-to-text conversion, speaker diarization, and sentiment scoring. The Voicera Difference: Voicera''s API stands out by adding behavioral analysis—decoding non-verbal cues like tone, facial expressions, and body language. This allows your platform to flag "likely true" or "likely untrue" statements for your users automatically.</p>
</div>

<div>
<div aria-hidden="true"></div>

