UPDATE public.blog_posts SET content = '<div>
<figure><img width="1030" height="584" src="https://voicera.io/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/7b11613f-eb24-49de-baa9-8d9b6ca86629-0000-1030x584.jpg" alt=""></figure>

<p>Voicera''s Video Intelligence API is revolutionizing how platforms analyze user-generated video content. By offering a data layer that detects sincerity, emotions, and intent with 30% greater accuracy than human judgment, we empower host platforms to deliver deeper insights to their end-users. This powerful engine integrates seamlessly into Sales Enablement, HR Tech, Legal, and Defense software, decoding non-verbal cues in real-time or from pre-recorded assets to add a new dimension of "Trust Analytics" to your application.<br></p>

<h2>What is a Video Intelligence API?</h2>

<div>
<div>
<p>A Video Intelligence API refers to advanced AI services that process video streams to extract insights— traditionally objects, actions, and basic sentiment. Voicera takes this further by focusing on behavioral analysis, using multimodal processing of face, voice, and body language to detect sincerity.<br></p>

<p>Voicera''s API distinguishes itself by providing "Credibility Scoring." Unlike general video APIs from major cloud providers that emphasize simple labeling or shot detection, Voicera prioritizes trust-building insights. We detect "likely true," "likely untrue," or neutral statements with approximately 78% accuracy, validated through rigorous testing. For platforms hosting high-stakes interactions, this means offering your users a superpower: the ability to see what isn''t being said.<br></p>
</div>

